# Quantiliom AI — Dashboard env (frontend only)
#
# Real credentials never belong in this repo. Use only public, non-secret
# values, and copy this file to .env.local (gitignored).
#
# The dashboard's Firebase Web config does NOT live here — it lives in
# src/lib/firebase-config.ts (gitignored). Copy
# src/lib/firebase-config.example.ts to that path and fill in the same
# values used by the website (Firebase Console → Project settings → Web
# app → SDK setup).
#
# Future variables (when integration deepens) will go here, e.g.:
#
# VITE_BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:5050
# VITE_WEBSITE_URL=http://localhost:5500
